shelton vineyards is a vineyard located in dobson, north carolina. of over 95 north carolina wineries, shelton vineyards is the largest family-owned estate winery in north carolina. located in the yadkin valley near mt. airy, the estate is 406-acre (1.64 km2) acres. the shelton vineyards' wines are reflective of the terroir of the yadkin valley. shelton vineyards has produced many award-winning wines.